    <div class="content"><p>Learn more about the PRT scam at  the <a href="http://www.roadkillbill.com/PRTisaJoke.html" rel="nofollow"> PRT is a Joke</a> web site.</p>
<p><a href="http://dumpmarkolson.blogspot.com/" rel="nofollow">Dump Representative Mark Olson (16b)</a></p>
</div>
